CdiVolDescVolumeSequenceNumber      # 4    ; Big endian only
CdiVolDescLogicalBlockSize          # 4    ; Big endian only
CdiVolDescPathTableSize             # 8    ; Big endian only
                                    # 8    ; Reserved
